raw_text = "~ start
## 11pm
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
do social_post(\"mabel_cram_study\")
do echo_set([\"182\"])
Mabel: Thought: 11pm already...
Mabel: Thought: I really need to sleep, got my presentation tomorrow
Mabel: Thought: What the heck is this \"sleep uniform\" supposed to be anyway??
Mabel: sfx2: bedcreakm1: *creak*
Mabel: Thought: I feel almost naked.. I wish I could wear my PJs instead
Mabel: Thought: Come on.. eyes closed and brain off
Mabel: Thought: Sleep... NOW!... NOW!! Hayaah!
Mabel: sfx2: bedcreakm3: *creak*
- [continue]
do echo_clear()
Mabel: Thought: This is SO not working... ugh
Mabel: sfx2: bedcreakm2: *creak*
Mabel: Thought: ...
Mabel: sfx2: bedcreakm1: *creak*
Mabel: sfx2: bedcreakm3: *creak*
Mabel: Thought: Oh you have GOT to be kidding me
Mabel: sfx2: bedcreakm4: *creak creak*
Mabel: Thought: Not again, it's so laaate 😩
Mabel: sfx3: coveredmoanm2: *mmf...*
Mabel: Thought: ...was that
Mabel: Thought: Nope. Not thinking about it. SLEEP TIME
Mabel: Thought: ...
Mabel: Thought: ....
Mabel: Thought: .....
- [continue]
do echo_clear()
Mabel: sfx2: bedcreakm2: *creak*
Mabel: sfx3: coveredmoanm1: *ahh...*
Mabel: Thought: ...that's DEFINITELY a girl
Mabel: Thought: So there really is someone in there with him
Mabel: PinkThought: What are they even doing to make a sound like that
Mabel: Thought: Stop it Mabel, that's so nosy!!
Mabel: Thought: But it's RIGHT there. How am I supposed to NOT hear it
Mabel: PinkThought: ...okay... juuust for a second
Mabel: PinkThought: Only because I'm awake anyway
Mabel: sfx3: coveredmoanm1: *ah..*
do echo_set([\"183\"])
Mabel: Thought: If I just... put my ear here...
Mabel: PinkThought: I can hear her really close...
Mabel: PinkThought: I really shouldn't be doing this
Mabel: sfx3: coveredmoanm3: *uhh..*
Mabel: PinkThought: She sounds like she's in pain??
Mabel: PinkThought: But... enjoying it!?
do heart(1)
- [continue]
do echo_clear()
do echo_set([\"184\"])
Mabel: PinkThought: Why is my heart going so fast
Mabel: PinkThought: I feel all warm and weird
Mabel: PinkThought: This is making me a little nauseous
Mabel: PinkThought: ...I-I can't keep listening to this
Mabel: sfx3: coveredmoanm2: *Mmh!*
Mabel: PinkThought: But I can't stop for some reason..
Mabel: sfx3: coveredmoanm3: *mmph*
Mabel: sfx3: coveredmoanm4: *ahh*
Mabel: Thought: ...ugh please just go to sleep already
Mabel: Thought: I can't take it anymore!
do heart(0)
Mabel: Thought: Go to sleep. Ignore it.
Mabel: Thought: ...
Mabel: PinkThought: I wonder if it'll happen again tomorrow...
- [continue]
do echo_clear()
do social_post(\"jason_club_closed_ntr\")
=> END"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
